duck: Tsao or Tsau is a village in North-West District of Botswana.

wiki.text:
'Tsao' or 'Tsau' is a village in North-West District of Botswana. It is located
close to the Okavango Delta and Lake Ngami. The population was 1,290 in 2001
census.<ref>{{cite web
 | url=http://www.cso.gov.bw/html/census/dist70_71_72_73.html title=Distribution
